gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 118, Warriors 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Warriors, 118-110. Caris LeVert recorded 22 points, five rebounds and four steals for the Cavaliers, while Donovan Mitchell added 21 points, seven rebounds and five assists in the victory. Stephen Curry tallied 30 points and four 3PM for the Warriors in the losing effort, while also tallying his 22,000th career point. The Cavaliers improve to 4-5 on the season, while the Warriors fall to 6-4.
